data.title: October 28th
data.text:
Anthony Fantano’s Birthday

Bold and brave, Fantano’s success comes from the hard work he has put in.

Joaquin Phoenix’s Birthday

Joaquin Phoenix had to lose 52 pounds for his part as the infamous Joker!

Matt Smith’s Birthday

From an aspiring football player to a rising actor, his career continues to thrive!

Trista Sutter’s Birthday

She found love, fame, and happiness, and she’s showing no sign of stopping.

Charlie Daniels’s Birthday

Charlie Daniels is one of the most accomplished musicians and songwriters to have ever lived.

Katherine Flores’s Birthday

Tattooing the stars is not enough. Katherine Flores is now part of the sky.

Brent Champagne’s Birthday

From flight attendant to reality show star! Here’s all you need to know about Mr. Champagne.

Caitlyn Jenner’s Birthday

This star was named Woman of the Year for her efforts to raise transgender awareness.

Brad Paisley’s Birthday

Brad Paisley composes most of his songs and often adds his sense of humor.

Brad Mondo’s Birthday

He is not only a phenomenal star hairstylist but also a social media personality and entrepreneur.

Bill Gates’s Birthday

Technology magnate and entrepreneur — he's one of the most famous technology personalities in the world.

Joy-Anna Duggar’s Birthday

The girl from the most controversial family on T.V. now has her own family.

Edd Gould’s Birthday

Edd Gould’s life may have been short but his legacy lives on to this day.

Julia Roberts’s Birthday

Today is the day of everyone’s favorite Hollywood actress, let us celebrate with her!

Frank Ocean’s Birthday

He is a phenomenal singer and songwriter who has revolutionized the R&B genre.

Lucy Bronze’s Birthday

Lucy Bronze has represented England at all levels, from under-11 up to the national team.

GamingWithJen’s Birthday

We cheer this skilled gamer who has tasted success in both the Roblox and Minecraft platforms!

Sheryl Underwood’s Birthday

The world wouldn't be nearly as hilarious without this comedian, actress, and television host.

Jasmine Rae’s Birthday

This country singer and songwriter continues to impress with her powerful performances and soul-touching music.
